---
import PublicLayout from '../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="Partnership Network"
  description="The smagile partnership network. Connecting agile professionals who share our values and commitment to quality."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-grey-900 dark:text-white">
      Partnership Network
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-8 prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-xl text-grey-700 dark:text-warm-200">
        Great outcomes often come from collaboration. The smagile partnership network connects
        independent agile professionals who share our values and commitment to quality.
      </p>

      <h2>Why a network?</h2>
      <p>
        No single consultant can be an expert in everything. When your challenges require
        specialist skills or additional capacity, we draw on trusted partners who we have
        worked with and can vouch for personally.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every partner in our network shares our commitment to integrity, practical support,
        and meeting teams where they are. We do not refer anyone we would not work alongside ourselves.
      </p>

      <h2>For consultants</h2>
      <p>
        If you are an independent agile professional and our values resonate with you,
        we would love to hear from you. We are always looking to connect with people who
        bring genuine expertise and a collaborative mindset.
      </p>

      <h2>Get involved</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="/contact/">Get in touch</a> to start a conversation about joining the network
        or to discuss how we might collaborate on an engagement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
